-- Waha Capital Second-Quarter Net Drops 90% to $1.6 Million as Revenue Falls
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-07-25T05:14:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/waha-capital-second-quarter-net-drops-90-to-1-6-million-as-revenue-falls.html

          
          
             Waha Capital PJSC, an Abu Dhabi
based leasing company, said second-quarter profit dropped to
5.99 million dirhams from 59.4 million dirhams a year-earlier,
according to a company statement to the Abu Dhabi bourse today.  
 Revenue fell to 97.3 million dirhams from 150.2 million
dirhams, it said.  
